.rules.mt-3.mb-5
  %h2 Rules
  %h3 Entering the contest
  %p In order to enter the contest, you must have your picture taken by monster bash staff after having received your wrist band. Contestants must stop by the Meeting Haus on Saturday, October 14, between the hours of 6 p.m. and 7:30 p.m. to be photographed. Those who show up too late cannot enter the contest.
  %h3 Voting
  %p Voting will take place through the GV Monster Bash website. Voting will be open from 8 p.m. to 10 p.m..
  %h3 Announcing the winners
  %p At 10:15 p.m. winners will be announced in the Fest Hall. If you are not present during the announcement you forfeit your prize
  %h3 Costume Guidelines
  %p.mb-3 No inappropriate costumes (racist, sexist, homophobic, too revealing, etc.) This is up to the judge’s discretion.
  %p.mb-3 No realistic looking weapons
  %p.mb-3 No messy costume attire that cannot be easily cleaned up or will cause damage to the facilities.


